<p>Squarespace SEO is not about the platform. It is about execution. 4.7 million sites run on Squarespace. 85% receive no organic traffic because their owners skip the fundamentals.</p>
<p>The top 10% prove what is possible. They compress images. They write meta descriptions. They publish consistently. They build links. They treat SEO as a discipline, not an afterthought.</p>
<p>You now have a complete playbook. Work through each section systematically. Fix the common mistakes first. Build content next. Earn links over time. Measure everything.</p>
<p>Squarespace gives you a solid foundation. What you build on it is up to you.</p>
